---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About">
  <div class="article-container">
    <h1 class="article-title">About Maze</h1>
    <div class="article-body">
      <p>
        Tech consulting is full of complex problems that look simple on the surface.
        Maze is a collection of articles, frameworks, and working AI agent prototypes
        that navigate these problems — showing both the thinking and the tooling.
      </p>
      <p>
        Every interactive component on this site is a working prototype, not a mockup. The
        goal is to demonstrate that AI-augmented approaches aren't a future-state vision — they're
        something you can build and use today.
      </p>
      <p>
        The content draws on 15+ years of delivery experience across government, energy, retail,
        and aviation sectors.
      </p>
      <p>
        Built by <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/YOUR_LINKEDIN/" target="_blank">Michael</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
